<template>
    <van-tabbar class="tag" route>
      <van-tabbar-item replace to="/home" icon="home-o">首页</van-tabbar-item>
      <van-tabbar-item replace to="/classes" icon="friends-o">我的班级</van-tabbar-item>
      <van-tabbar-item icon="label-o">助教监督</van-tabbar-item>
      <van-tabbar-item icon="user-o">个人中心</van-tabbar-item>
    </van-tabbar>
</template>

<script>
import Vue from "vue";
import { Tabbar, TabbarItem } from "vant";

Vue.use(Tabbar)
  .use(TabbarItem);
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      active: "home"
    };
  }
};
</script>

<style>
.tag{
  position: relative;
  bottom: 0
}
</style>
